reviews.review_text: best McDonalds I have ever had -5 year old son
Great location, staff here works hard keeping the place clean. First McDs Ive been in for the last 6 months that had a dry clean washroom floor, even around the fixtures!
Very quick and efficient service they have. 3 self order machines are there and huge dining area. Nice view and at good location.
For McDonalds food it was good, Loved the service fast and very friendly. Parking: There is a reasonable amount of parking Food : 5/5 |
They have the best soft serve here. I visit other locations ans you can tell when the machine isnt cleaned regularly. But this location cleans it often. Good job mcds
The old school restaurant has lots of room for everything.

One of the most fanciest McDonalds Ive ever been too. They use automatic machines to do the ordering. You basically select what you one, finish the order, pay by card or get the ticket and pay at the counter. They also do make your own gourmet burger. I was quite skeptical about this, but I must say Im quite impressed with the quality of the burger. The beef patty was juicy and the rest of the ingredients were fresh. Its a bit pricier compared to the usual menu, but totally worth it. I dont generally eat McDonalds but if I do, Id definitely find one that do make your own burger.
I love the place, the crews, the atmosphere but its just their big mac, patties are already thin and lettuce chopped up.
Classic Macdonalds. Easily accessible for me and the staff are always busy but they are nice.
I personally work here i love the environment over here and each and every person is very friendly so far .

The system was rebooting. Couldn t place orders for 45 mins. Manager heard my woes and was able to push my mobile order through. Really appreciated it. It was 4 mins from breakfast service so they really helped last min.
Service is super quick. Cannot recommend enough.
Love their food ,service and their excellent way of dealing with their customers

Really nice service. Always ready with the order for Skipthedishes delivery driver. Not like other McDonalds locations where we have to wait for long. Awesome place and dependable service. The servers are so nice and friendly. Good job team.
Great service but lots of not very smart people that parks the trucks here. And blocks the whole parking lot.
Clean , nice service, ice cream available, lots of seating space outside and inside . Looks like a safe harbor for passing by travelers and local visitors. Parking: Not too many parking spots

I go here for lunch when I m working nearby this McDonald s. The food has always been fresh so I m very pleased with this location. The guy who runs food to waiting vehicles is absolutely awesome he deserves a raise!! September 15th 12:05   2022
Love it all. Great burgers.
Staff is great and deserve more money/employee support and assistance Program. If i am CEO/owner...would build a City free rent. Employees pay utilities/taxes/service.
Old lady s iced coffee is best in Vancouver
Consistently the best most reliable and friendliest McDonalds. Management should be proud and recognized.

Was helped my Karam, he was amazing!! Very personable. He gave us well above & beyond the service Im used to from this place. I think he has a bright future with McDonalds or anywhere else he so chooses with that can do attitude :)

Busier location but well run. Drive thru while almost always busy moves quickly, friendly, and efficiently. One of the few McDonalds that actually made my boyfriends bigmac just like the picture. Only issue I have had is the people who block ongoing traffic on Boundary instead of turning the corner and entering from Broadway, but this is not the stores fault just bad drivers and covid increasing drive thru capacity.

It was a very  nice staff that  I ever met. You can imagine a very hot night,   every  one wanted.... ice cream, pop, ice coffee.... But the staff are so nice from the cashier ( cheerful voice , friendly, and very professional staff) All people who  are working there will making you know you will be  taking  care of because  they an un unique group. Iam strongly recommend  Mcdonald of Broadway and Boundary. Please  invite yourself. So that you will  have a good  experience just like us. Best wishes.  And enjoy  what GOD send to us( nice weather,  best place to live in this planet).
So clean!! Every 10 min they are cleaning tables. Serving so politely and fast. Great store and workers
Its McDonalds... food is as expected, service was fine, a little slow, but it was late night and just the drive through.

Just went here and tried the seriously chicken got it crispy with tomato and mozz, I was honestly impressed it didnt feel like a fast food burger, well put together nice flavours real ingredients. I always used to see McDonalds as fast, nothing special food. I feel differently now!
Really fast service. Fries were great. As a person who cant eat meat, thats sadly the only thing I can really judge.

This is the fastest McDonalds that Ive been to. From the time that they took my order and received it, I only had to wait 6min if not less quite impressed of there service as well how hot and fresh the food was. I would recomend this McDonalds to anyone going to that area lol.
Its a good place sometimes if we dont have other choices. We can sit in Macdonald to get together and talk about something to do etc. Food is also reasonable and delicious

I ordered from here at 1 in the morning for delivery and the service was amazingly fast the food wasnt thrown together sloppily and they even put in a cookie for free this place in my opinion for delivery and quality of food deserves a 5 star thank you McDonalds Ill definitely buy more stuff from here again.
I love this place to visit perfect for the whole family

One of the best Mcdonald - Lots of parking space - Quick Drive thru and you know what to expect from Mcdonald - delicious but fattening fast food at affordable prices. I dont actually know what people are complaining about regarding the food they serve. I dont feel like they are any worst than other burger joints - fries and burgers is just not the most healthy. This is for sure one of the bigger Mcdonalds and its close to the entrance to the highway. I come here quite a bit, always the same - always clean and good service.
Karam was the nicest employee Ive met at a McDonalds, but everyone is great. Fastest and most accurate McDonalds of the 3 near me
Not much wait at the drive through.  Customer service was great.  Enjoyed the mango pineapple drink.
fast.. order fresh fries and mc chicken.. they werent rude about it.. told me to dear down and brought my food to the table.. great service.
The guy I ordered from at the window loaded up my ice cream cone and was overall really nice. Hes an employee of the month, not a Dave!
This location does a really good job. Mornings are always crowded and super busy, however they always greet you with a smile and remember you if you re a repeat customer.

Fast service...!  Good Mcfood....! I saw a girl ask if they were hiring....guy 10 steps away asks her to come around.... By the time my order was done the girl was already getting a crash course of operations....hired on the spot...!!  Wow..! Im Lovin It...!    M
Best McDonalds Ive been to, I live in Langley and they all always warm/cold, this place seems always fresh. Theyre doing something right here.
Quick and fast. Staff were friendly and helpful when showing them coupons that I was having a hard time figuring out on the phone app.
Great service. Fast drive through. No communication issues
when we have coupons,  otherwise  a little bit overpriced.  My favorite is fish burger,  if no coupon is $6, and sizes like a mini cheese burger,
Very good
Our favorite place to get breakfast. Great staff and always very friendly to our Goldwing club members . Lots of parking
Very clean. Everything was made correctly. Not even regular restaurants can manage that one.  McDonalds is soooo much better than it used to be
Excellent customer service. BEST ICED COFFEE. I always get iced coffees on different McDonalds and this branch has the best iced coffee!!
Marg & Marlyn always provide friendly, fast & efficient service. Lunchtime can get busy !
Very helpful staff, and the food was very good.
Great place for any meal or snack and breakfast any time.   $5.00 double cheese burger meal is a favourite and free coffee with filled coffee card.

I lost my cell phone during the lunchtime at this restaurant , however I find it back after 2 hours when I come back to ask them , I really appreciated any of their staffs or anybody who picked up my cell phone and hand in to front counter , otherwise, I would have a bad weekend
Chicken nuggets and coffee was great.Quick service.The place was very spacious, 2 min walking distance from bus stop.
Good place for quick takeaway. Service is good and staff is working in and out to offer best service for takeaways.
I only went to the drive through but the employees were very enthusiastic and upbeat and the food was good.
Roomy usual McDonalds. Has a drive-thru. Also they have disabled   parking and wheelchair accessible entrance.
Kind and accommodating staff, the food is as good as any McDonalds around
Always good value for the money. The mobile ordering is a good idea but you need to add the coupons.
Yummy McDonald s fries   lol I like their fries   lol drove through just for the fries   lol
Good location, lots of seating areas and flat parking to make easy access for seniors.
Fast service and friendly staff.. this McDonalds is way better than others...
Lots of indoor seating, some outdoor seating, usually very clean.
Fries came out too salty, called in and they immediately remedied the problem amazing customer service, literally made it no issue.
better than the renfrew mcdonalds by a long shot if you can drive its worth the extra 5 minutes or so.
Hi   I have a question for you is fine with me but I dont know if I can help in any way I can get a ride to the house
The staff is very helpful and patient
Its a great place for my kids and I. Employees are friendly there too. Great service and lots of parking.
Quiet
Friendly staff, accommodating of food requests. They have wifi and TVs to watch the hockey game!
Good place for burger, fries and a pop. Friendly staff and service is quick and good.
Great location. Lots of parking. Spacious interior. Typical McDonalds food.
Loved the direct ordering screen, much easier and correct than using a person
Friendly staff and they provide my breakfast  most days always remember my order
Clean and quick just like a fast food chain is suppose to be.
Always a good go to for every country your visiting. Bagel breakfast sandwiches are a must try in Canada.
Drive through lane is a tiny bit awkward. Otherwise, this is a great location!
Friendly crew, great customer service and definitely would like to visit again.
Staff friendly  could improve Car service  especially in Early  morning
I always go to this location as they have great customer service.
Lots of parking space (busy during lunch hours). They have outside eating area too.
Love it. Looks old school, reminds me of 90s Mickie Ds.
Easy to order and friendly staff
Fast service with a lot of options. Also, place an order yourself using automatic machines
Beautiful bear sightings ;)
Its a exactly what you expect. Good food and good service for a good price.
Special occasions place for my family
The staff at this location is definitely why I like it so much
Fast service and a great smoothie.
Nice staff
I like McDs! Always my fav for fast food convenience.

Very busy but still was able to maintain good service.
Fast service. No kids playfround but a nice area to sit outside.
Quick drive through good food small parking lot
Lovely place to sit and have some quality time with friends.
Great customer service and very affordable prices
The MC griddles good for your hang over lol
Fast and friendly service and clean dining room area.
Love their coffee
Used the screen to order. Delivered the food to the table including my drink.
